# Step 2 – Verify the Installation Package

The Splunk Enterprise installation package was confirmed to be present on the Ubuntu Server.

### Command

```bash
ls
```

### Screenshot

**Insert Screenshot 2 here**

*Caption:* Splunk Enterprise installation package available on the Ubuntu Server.

