# Outcome

Splunk Enterprise was successfully installed and configured on the Ubuntu Server virtual machine. The SIEM platform was verified to be operational, configured to start automatically during system boot, and accessible through the web interface from the Windows 10 virtual machine. This completes the deployment of the centralized SIEM server for the SOC Detection and Monitoring Lab.

